Feature: Have a green CI/CD
    As a busy developer
    I want to push my code in main with no fear and stress
    So that I always know that the test are green and the codebase is clean

    Acceptance Criteria:
    - Have a CI/CD pipeline ✅
    - Have the remote quality gates to check the tests are green ✅
    - Have the remote quality gates to check the codebase is healthy ✅
    - Break the pipeline is the code is smelly or the test are red ✅
    - Get notified if the pipeline id broken ✅